{"type": "article", "id": 30177, "title": "凑齐火烈鸟一家，喝个下午茶｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-07-26T23:02:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 30214, "name": "Saif Faisal"}, {"id": 30678, "name": "Studioforma"}, {"id": 30679, "name": "Meroni & Colzani"}, {"id": 30680, "name": "Notabag"}, {"id": 30681, "name": "FormNation"}, {"id": 30682, "name": "Uberliss"}, {"id": 22998, "name": "Alessandro Zambelli"}, {"id": 30683, "name": "Roxanne Flick"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160804171028ifxKeMgn4BbGjN3Y.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Marqué by Alessandro Zambelli</h3><p>来自意大利的工业设计师 <a href=\"http://www.alessandrozambelli.it/designstudio/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alessandro Zambelli</a> 最近参加了伦敦创意画廊 <a href=\"http://www.matterofstuff.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Matter of Stuff</a> 举办的设计师驻外培训比赛，他的参赛作品是一套致敬了 1920 年代的巴黎以及装饰艺术的家具系列 Marqué，其中包括吧台、柜子以及咖啡桌。Zambelli 对材料以及造型都进行了重新思考，让新型表达形式与传统工艺进行融合。家具的表面嵌入了大量交错的图案，与金属表面不同程度的氧化一起展现出了装饰艺术的多样性和微妙感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232501fJqrpT10zOVe8FaC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.597800\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232502RLUEOlB4DefT3dQk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607262325014etAqh7QoaPHWvwc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705379\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232502yrTHwA3ixRQPbeCY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232502KQBAkxzutSqVJZeL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564792\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232502X4GJdt9pi1HcMS3x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563570\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>PAM by Studioforma</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.studioforma.ch/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studioforma</a> 最近为意大利品牌 <a href=\"http://www.meroniecolzani.it/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Meroni &amp; Colzani</a> 设计了一款具有热带风情的椅子 <a href=\"http://www.sfdesignlab.com/pile_portfolio/pam/\" rel=\"nofollow\">PAM</a>，流畅的线条以及管状结构使它看上去就好像是一张巨大的棕榈叶。椅子由工匠在以家具生产而闻名的布里安扎地区（Brianza）采用核桃木手工制作而成，椅腿和座位之间无缝相连，整体造型简洁优雅。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607262325230Nl52zy94mGrWVZL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.610000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232522oLBsp2A0mxMraFWc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.698333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232522uMFega6QKVbx3dq1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.688333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232523OQ93fLl1UTNKC6EY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232523vkQNpytRbSCHm7Az.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232524Nb0iY4lpygqkEoa7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Counterpoise lamp by Saif Faisal</h3><p>我们曾经介绍过印度工作室 <a href=\"http://www.saif-faisal.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saif Faisal</a> 推出的一款<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/29629.html\">灯具</a>，他们的新作 <a href=\"http://www.saif-faisal.com/counterpoise-lamp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Counterpoise</a> 台灯同样具有能够随意进行调节的特点。这款灯具的设计灵感来源于日本一种被称为 Magewappa 的曲木工艺，木制的圆形灯罩带给人一种自然温暖的感觉。黑色的灯柱将灯罩与光滑的底座连接在一起，并没有额外采用五金零件，使整体造型显得十分流畅。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232411qEZuMrsAL4NQjf0i.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.806667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232411tP4gpq6onW710QLz.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607262324113q6raFiBSehbmxTY.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.376667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232411d9NaYxfIgXqyPScK.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.251135\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232411D95JrQRAyvTtGOSE.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.290000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232412uBvqOoSKXNg3Ltjb.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.247863\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Reflective Notabag by Notabag</h3><p>2013 年，Adnan Alicusic 设计了一款既能当作背包又可以折叠成小口袋的购物袋 <a href=\"http://www.notabag.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Notabag</a>，这个独一无二的产品不仅在众筹上获得了成功，还赢得了 2016 年的德国设计奖的杰出产品设计奖。今天要介绍的 Reflective Notabag 是它的迭代产品，为了更好地在夜晚保护使用者的安全，为购物袋加入了反光材料。起初这只是 Notabag 与瑞典的自行车配件品牌 <a href=\"http://www.bookman.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">BOOKMAN</a> 合作的限量产品，在收到不错的反馈之后，它们决定进行大批量生产，并且为这个系列加入了更多的颜色选择。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/adnanalicusic/be-seen-be-safe-the-reflective-bag-and-backpack\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 25 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232352SdGRfc9mPWN2Xp5a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.550000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016072623235290h6uH4dOyAErZxM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.501471\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232352Hh7WDOKrznTj4q2l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560178\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232352AelQztgE6sRPfDiI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.555391\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232352Cx6BTkgFzt1PYy84.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.073529\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Purpur by Roxanne Flick</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.roxanneflick.com/purpur_en.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purpur</a> 是德国普福尔茨海姆大学（Pforzheim University）毕业生 <a href=\"http://www.roxanneflick.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Roxanne Flick</a> 的作品，她将火烈鸟从水中捕鱼的过程与人们滤茶的方式联系在了一起。茶壶和糖罐的出水口被设计成像是火烈鸟脖子一样弯曲的形状，与它们圆鼓鼓的“身材”结合在一起，看上去生动活泼。Purpur 采用粉浆浇注法烧制而成，随后分别注入淡灰色和粉色的颜料。Flick 还为茶杯设计了配套的橡木制杯座，用这样一组就好像是小火烈鸟一样的茶具泡茶喝，仿佛空气中充溢的茶香也更加清甜了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232325APUTheLQE2ik0Bcp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232325WMLcqx2YyGFlB6rE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.048077\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607262323256cnSiK8MPeVRrvbC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232325FubKxXnJysiDmvTL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232325BE7A2zwa8VWgoQ51.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Uberliss by FormNation</h3><p>如果你不曾被专业护发产品的包装惊艳到，设计公司 <a href=\"http://formnation.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">FormNation</a> 这次为来自美国伊利诺斯州的 Uberliss 全新打造的包装设计或许会让你忍不住驻足端详。黑白两种底色分别代表了针对发廊以及普通用户的两种产品线，上面印有专门设计的手绘图案。这些看上去非常随性的涂鸦其实代表着产品不同的功效，带给人一种耳目一新的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232310Crq501j78PVsALZf.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232306Q2mANfJUpwdteaFS.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.557000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232307Qy5gIUdVD0sp1JlS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232308k3QTgdeKBFrSJL0u.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.435000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232309wuO84ZAnGIe36MjR.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232309dUGTXLOzE0ClI9KM.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}